    <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>

    <name>TowerDefense</name>
    <description>
        Tower defense is a subgenre of strategy video game where the goal is to defend a player's territories or
        possessions by obstructing the enemy attackers, usually achieved by placing defensive structures on or along
        their path of attack.
    </description>

